Muzvidzidzo zve[[Kupimanzvimbo]] (Geometry) [[gonya]] (angle) izwi rinoreva kushama kwakaita mukwava uri pakati pemitsetse miviri inosangana pamukwava iwoyo. Kukura kwegonya kunopimwa nenhamwe yekushama kwakaita mukwava uri pakati pemitsetse miviri, gonya rinokura kana mitsetse apo iyi inenge iri kutaramukana.


Gonya kana ichipimwa inopimwa nechiyero chinonzi dhigiriyi (<sup>o</sup>). Mitsetse miviri kana ichinge yabatana inenge ine mupimo wegonya  0<sup>o</sup>. Mitsetse kana yakaita mutwi (yakarurama) inenge ine mupimo wegonya 90<sup>o</sup>. Gonya rinopoteredza [[chimiso]] rinopimwa kuita 360<sup>o</sup>.
